 108:src/voice.h   **** // в”Ђв”Ђ Voice 2: open power-chord bass в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв
 109:src/voice.h   **** //   Same chord stack as VOICE_BASS, but the filter starts brighter and sweeps
